{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20260503/s00024/c0b4a0c4da05482697a0fd5eefcfc902.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:1em\">\n    <p>內地民眾趁五一長假出遊，各地均見享受假期的人潮。各地亦舉辦不同活動，人們樂享假日時光。本圖輯帶讀者感受內地五一濃厚假日氣氛民間煙火氣。</p>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-03T04:57:31.010346+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":67,"images":1,"source":"明報 消閒","fallback":"none"}}